# Build-context filter for the enrichment image, which builds from the REPO ROOT
# (docker-compose: build.context: .). BuildKit prefers this file (next to the
# Dockerfile) over the root .dockerignore. Keep the context tiny: the root
# workspace manifest, the enrichment member, and the rpg-config package it links.
*
!package.json
!enrichment
!packages
# Heavy / irrelevant bits inside the allowed paths.
**/node_modules
**/.git
debug-data
packages/fast-image-processing
packages/jwt-user-auth
